{"tid":425942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"球迷再噓國歌    饒戈平：盡快立國歌法，是否追溯，看香港法律具體規定","createTime":"2017-10-06T07:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T08:41:19.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f4a0420cf8c120fadaa87f5405134ec148e6414d","tid":425942,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:32:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171006/s00001/653bdb4bfc5d06a0dbaf5aa158ede4d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171006%2Fs00001%2F653bdb4bfc5d06a0dbaf5aa158ede4d8.jpg&h=c834b32d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港足球代表隊昨晚在旺角大球場友賽老撾，最終在現場2029名球迷前，以4比0大勝對手。不過，現場開賽前奏起中國國歌時，有部分球迷立即發出噓聲及舉不文手勢，足總主席梁孔德今天回應《明報》查詢時表示，噓國歌行為是足總所不能控制，希望球迷自律。<br />\n<br />\n梁孔德指，足總過往已就噓國歌行為作出多次呼籲，希望球迷自律。他亦表示，目前仍未知道在場亞洲足協監場人員的反應，及會否採取行動；也未知道若作出懲罰，是否會比起上次更加嚴重。至於港隊下周二（10日）迎戰馬來西亞的亞洲盃外圍賽，梁則指噓國歌行為是足總所不能控制，屆時亦不會採取措施阻止，再次呼籲球迷自律。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，全國港澳研究會副會長饒戈平接受電子傳媒訪問時表示，本港要盡快就《國歌法》本地立法，並指「在沒有立法以前，這些違法行為會被紀錄在案的。是不是要再被追溯，要看香港法律具體規定。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，饒戈平亦反問，明知噓國歌違法而照做的行為是「對法律的尊重呢，還是破壞呢？」，呼籲港人反思是否要以「包容、縱容、姑且」的態度對待這些行為，而非依法辦理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171006/s00001/1507273902235\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171006%2Fs00001%2F1507273902235&d=RkDpb%2Fugp%2FKDARkKXTmhTo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=81eb92e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171006%2Fs00001%2F1507273902235&h=83f51593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171006/s00001/1507273902235</a>"},{"pid":"9a8f8591245390f1b6a5df93781c5827d7157c7e","tid":425942,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:39:55.000Z","msg":"由CCTVB重點報導開始<br />\n劇本已經啟動"},{"pid":"bdecd55e0365fad93a9e5e3ff0e69950abf41f1a","tid":425942,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:46:44.000Z","msg":"以後都閉門作賽啦，屌你老母死足總。"},{"pid":"ab0d4f362673eae56ce50ba421217cdef521d478","tid":425942,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:47:41.000Z","msg":"係場外算唔算犯法？"},{"pid":"79d6de4cd75275656f52e1e7f0b518c7ce0b65b5","tid":425942,"uid":2521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:51:02.000Z","msg":"平時唔係叫人要包容、和諧咩？<br />\n做咩而家又唔包容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0379c726aea6b429eabfa128828bf04e726427d1","tid":425942,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:51:29.000Z","msg":"係咪全部拉晒？"},{"pid":"1a695fee92c8031890dac78ca21b73f1176309be","tid":425942,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:55:50.000Z","msg":"都估到仆街中港共想立國歌法"},{"pid":"46082b70e8e357ea6927d33863699cdaa1509e3d","tid":425942,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:56:46.000Z","msg":"留名睇人blame the victim 話噓支那歌比共匪有位入你"},{"pid":"a26faff24caee483e55706027de93c6b6fc97c51","tid":425942,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:58:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名睇人blame the victim 話噓支那歌比共匪有位入你</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住中共仆街咩都做得出"},{"pid":"6647fa9637b757333826853a1c5ab39686fba7e4","tid":425942,"uid":37798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:59:28.000Z","msg":"噓自己都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c377b368053a6085425210f012d3cd8bd532ddc2","tid":425942,"uid":10438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:01:32.000Z","msg":"好驚，以後起国歌去廁所算"},{"pid":"1fb7ac6e5346c948f0dfe5043ea3f9648e9cdb51","tid":425942,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc